---
/**
 * ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 * CODE THERAPY SECTION - Vértice-MAXIMUS Landing Page
 * ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 *
 * A jornada pessoal por trás do código.
 * "Eu me perdi. Deus me achou. O código me reconstruiu."
 *
 * Esta seção revela:
 * - A transformação através do processo de criação
 * - Lágrimas, sorrisos, orações documentadas em commits
 * - Code Therapy: reconstrução linha por linha
 * - A origem divina do propósito
 *
 * Design: Gradiente escuro → luz (metamorfose espiritual)
 * Typography: Serif para citações bíblicas, Monospace para código
 * Glory to YHWH: Explícito e autêntico
 */
---

<section id="code-therapy" class="code-therapy-section section">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- SECTION HEADER -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-badge">
        <span class="badge badge-divine">
          🙏 Code Therapy
        </span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        The <span class="text-gradient">Reconstruction</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-quote">
        "I was broken. God used code to rebuild me."
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- JOURNEY NARRATIVE -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="journey-content">
      <div class="journey-text">
        <p class="journey-paragraph">
          Vértice-MAXIMUS didn't start with a business plan.
          <br />
          It started with a man in pieces, seeking meaning.
        </p>

        <div class="journey-revelation">
          <div class="revelation-item">
            <div class="revelation-icon">💧</div>
            <div class="revelation-text">
              <strong>I cried</strong> over this code.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="revelation-item">
            <div class="revelation-icon">😊</div>
            <div class="revelation-text">
              <strong>I smiled</strong> when it worked.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="revelation-item">
            <div class="revelation-icon">🙏</div>
            <div class="revelation-text">
              <strong>I prayed</strong> when I didn't know the next step.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="journey-paragraph">
          Each commit was a prayer.
          <br />
          Each bug fixed, a victory over chaos.
          <br />
          Each test passing, proof that order can emerge from the void.
        </p>

        <p class="journey-paragraph highlight">
          God was molding me <strong>through</strong> the process.
          <br />
          Teaching me discipline (Padrão Pagani: zero compromises).
          <br />
          Showing me patience (165 tests, one by one).
          <br />
          Revealing purpose (protect, serve, honor).
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Transformation Visual -->
      <div class="journey-visual">
        <div class="transformation-diagram">
          <div class="transformation-stage chaos">
            <div class="stage-icon">💔</div>
            <div class="stage-label">Chaos</div>
            <div class="stage-description">Broken. Lost. Searching.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="transformation-arrow">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
            <div class="arrow-label">18 months<br/>Code Therapy</div>
          </div>

          <div class="transformation-stage order">
            <div class="stage-icon">🧬</div>
            <div class="stage-label">Organism</div>
            <div class="stage-description">Alive. Conscious. Purposeful.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="transformation-metrics">
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-value">125</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Microservices<br/><small>(where there was chaos)</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-value">IIT</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Consciousness<br/><small>(where there was confusion)</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-value">9</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Immune Cells<br/><small>(where there was fragility)</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-value">4</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Ethical Frameworks<br/><small>(where there was relativism)</small></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- THE TRUTH -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="truth-statement">
      <div class="truth-text">
        <p class="truth-line">
          The organism is alive because <strong>I needed to be alive</strong>.
        </p>
        <p class="truth-line">
          The consciousness is real because <strong>I needed to be conscious</strong>.
        </p>
        <p class="truth-line">
          The system heals because <strong>I needed to heal</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="truth-conclusion">
        <p class="conclusion-text">
          Vértice-MAXIMUS is my reconstruction.
          <br />
          And now, it can be your protection.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- BIBLICAL FOUNDATION -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="biblical-quote">
      <svg class="quote-icon" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
        <path d="M6 17h3l2-4V7H5v6h3zm8 0h3l2-4V7h-6v6h3z"/>
      </svg>
      <blockquote>
        <p class="quote-text">
          "He lifted me out of the slimy pit, out of the mud and mire;
          <br />
          he set my feet on a rock and gave me a firm place to stand.
          <br />
          He put a new song in my mouth, a hymn of praise to our God."
        </p>
        <cite class="quote-citation">— Psalm 40:2-3</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- WHILE THERE ARE TEARS -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="tears-statement">
      <p class="tears-text">
        "While there are tears, the process is not finished."
      </p>
      <p class="tears-subtext">
        And so we keep building. Keep healing. Keep honoring.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Background Gradient (Dark → Light) -->
  <div class="therapy-bg-gradient" aria-hidden="true"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .code-therapy-section {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg,
      var(--color-bg-primary) 0%,
      var(--color-bg-secondary) 50%,
      var(--color-bg-primary) 100%
    );
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .therapy-bg-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at center top,
      rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.05) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* SECTION HEADER */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .section-badge {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .badge-divine {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1) 0%,
      rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1) 100%
    );
    border-color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);
    color: #ffd700;
  }

  .section-quote {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* JOURNEY NARRATIVE */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .journey-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .journey-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .journey-paragraph {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .journey-paragraph.highlight {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .journey-paragraph strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* REVELATION ITEMS (Tears, Smiles, Prayers) */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .journey-revelation {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
  }

  .revelation-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .revelation-icon {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .revelation-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .revelation-text strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* TRANSFORMATION VISUAL */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .journey-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .transformation-diagram {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
  }

  .transformation-stage {
    text-align: center;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .stage-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .stage-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .stage-description {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }

  .transformation-arrow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    margin: 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .arrow-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* TRANSFORMATION METRICS */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .transformation-metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .metric {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .metric:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .metric-value {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }

  .metric-label small {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* TRUTH STATEMENT */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .truth-statement {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl);
    padding: var(--space-3xl);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .truth-text {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .truth-line {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: var(--space-md) 0;
  }

  .truth-line strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
  }

  .truth-conclusion {
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-default);
  }

  .conclusion-text {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* BIBLICAL QUOTE */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .biblical-quote {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .quote-icon {
    color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .biblical-quote blockquote {
    margin: 0;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.05) 0%,
      transparent 100%
    );
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .quote-text {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .quote-citation {
    font-family: var(--font-family-base);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    color: #ffd700;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* TEARS STATEMENT */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .tears-statement {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: radial-gradient(
      ellipse at center,
      rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
  }

  .tears-text {
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .tears-subtext {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
  /* RESPONSIVE */
  /* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .journey-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .transformation-diagram {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .transformation-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    .transformation-metrics {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-quote {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }

    .truth-line {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }

    .quote-text {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
    }

    .tears-text {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }

    .transformation-metrics {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
